<p>This week your two favorite geeks tackle your questions about USB disconnects, &quot;no Internet connection&quot; reports, creating short video clips from long segments, and when (and whether!) to buy new or look for refurb/used. Listen as John and Dave talk you through all of this and much, much more. Press play, download, and enjoy learning at least five new things!Note: Shownotes are complete!</p>
